V0019_01_00_00_0.text: You're trapped and the doors are locked!

V0019_01_00_01_0.text: Fail to navigate our maze correctly...

V0019_01_00_01_1.text: To the land of defeat we send you directly!

V0019_01_00_02_0.text: If you desire to pass our chamber...

V0019_01_00_02_1.text: You must agree to face the danger!

V0019_01_00_03_1.text: Be lost in our laybrinth forever!

V0019_03_00_00_0.text: You don't know when to quit.

V0019_05_00_00_0.text: We will get the card we need!

V0019_05_00_00_1.text: Such a fact is true indeed! I draw!

V0019_07_09_00_0.text: I flip over my face-down card!

V0019_08_00_00_0.text: Teams are only as strong as their weakest link, and that link is you!

V0019_08_00_00_1.text: Face the wall-warping power of Magical Labyrinth!

V0019_08_00_01_0.text: I activate the Spell Card, Tribute Doll!

V0019_08_00_01_1.text: I can activate it by Tributing one monster on my field!

V0019_08_00_04_0.text: I activate the Equip Spell, Fairy Meteor Crush!

V0019_08_00_07_0.text: Witness the fearsome card I drew!

V0019_08_00_08_0.text:
Time to shut your yap!
With my card, Remove Trap!

V0019_08_00_10_0.text:
Heh heh heh...
The maze holds even more terrors for you!

V0019_08_00_11_0.text:
I activate my Trap Card!
Judgment of Anubis!

V0019_08_00_12_0.text: There is no exit to my maze, I swear!

V0019_08_00_12_1.text: With the Trap Card, Labyrinth of Nightmare!

V0019_09_00_02_0.text: Sanga of the Thunder's effect activates!

V0019_09_00_03_1.text: Reflect the attack with Tidal Shield!

V0019_11_00_00_0.text: I Summon a monster in Attack Position!

V0019_11_00_01_0.text: I Summon a monster in Attack Position!

V0019_11_01_00_0.text: I Summon a monster in Defense Position!

V0019_11_01_01_0.text: I Summon a monster in Defense Position!

V0019_13_00_00_0.text: Your next step in the maze will leave you in a daze!

V0019_13_00_02_0.text:
This is the beginning of the end! 
I summon Kazejin, God of Wind!

V0019_13_00_03_0.text:
Sanga of the Thunder!
Let's take 'em under!

V0019_13_00_04_0.text:
Here comes Suijin!
The Water God!

V0019_13_00_05_0.text:
Elements of thunder, water and wind! 
Sanga, Suijin, Kazejin begin!

V0019_13_00_05_1.text: Meld your powers in eternal light! Show these fools your unstoppable might!

V0019_13_00_06_0.text:
Emerging from the floor!
My Labyrinth Wall!

V0019_13_00_07_0.text: Is it too cruel if I summon Shadow Ghoul?

V0019_13_00_08_0.text: Wall Shadow will turn your monsters into smears on the labyrinth walls!

V0019_13_00_10_0.text: Dungeon Worm! Rise to the surface!

V0019_13_00_11_0.text:
I shall play this card!
Monster Tamer!

V0019_13_00_12_0.text:
Ah! This is the card I need!
Giga-Tech Wolf!

V0019_19_00_09_0.text: My Labyrinth Tank is within striking range!

V0019_19_00_10_0.text: Dungeon Worm is burrowing right towards you!

V0019_21_00_20_0.text:
My turn is over!
It's your turn!

V0019_28_00_00_0.text:
Hahaha!
Against us, you cannot defend!

V0019_28_00_00_1.text: All your life points we did rend!

V0019_28_00_02_0.text:
Hahahaha!
This duel we did win!

V0019_28_00_03_1.text: We’ll mark your graves with your inscription!

V0019_29_00_00_1.text: How did you find the light out of our maze?

V0019_29_00_01_0.text:
You fool!
This opponent you failed to halt!

V0019_29_00_01_1.text:
Don't look at me! 
It's not my fault!

V0019_29_00_02_0.text: How could our tag team fail?

V0019_29_00_02_1.text: This brings a sad end to our tale!

V0019_30_00_00_0.text:
The correct path is behind one of two doors.
Will your choice be good or poor?

V0019_30_00_01_0.text: Hurry up and choose a door!

V0019_33_00_00_0.text: Our teamwork is second to none!

V0019_33_00_01_0.text: Learn the horrors of the maze!

V0019_34_00_00_0.text: The Paradox Brothers' function is to guard this underground dungeon!

V0019_34_00_01_0.text:
If you cherish your lives, choose my way.
No. Select my side or you’ll pay!

V0019_34_00_02_0.text:
Hahaha. Keep up the good fight.
It is our pleasure to extinguish your light.

V0019_34_00_04_0.text: If the maze you do not clear, victory will never come near!

V0019_34_00_05_0.text: Your bond of friendship is too poor to open the labyrinth's door!

V0019_34_00_06_0.text:
Hahaha!
You fell right into my trap!

V0019_34_00_07_0.text:
Heh heh...
I drew a terrifying card.

V0019_35_00_00_0.text:
A team like no other!
We are the Paradox Brothers!

V0019_35_00_01_0.text:
You are in for a shock!
When facing the Brothers Paradox!

V0019_26_00_02_0.text: That the best you can do?

V0019_36_00_01_0.text:
Hahahaha!
I leave the rest to you!

V0019_36_00_02_0.text: The rest is up to you.

V0019_36_00_04_0.text:
Argh!
You need to turn this Duel around!

V0019_36_00_05_0.text:
Oof...
Get me out of this mess!
